        following conditions. The following definitions shall have the same meaning regardless of
        whether they appear in singular or in plural.
      </p>

      <h2>Collection and Use of Your Personal Data</h2>
      <p>
        We collect personal data to provide and improve our Service. By using the Service, You agree
        to the collection and use of information in accordance with this Privacy Policy.
      </p>

